ntent/uploads/2019/08/fuguohaobushijizhe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinanewscenter.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Ffuguohaobushijizhe.jpg&h=f37fd1e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"改名喺內地好常見，同風水有關，英文名FUHAO=富豪「rich」，佢同銀行工作人員話自己英文名係「FUHAO」就得，銀行有刻度機，可以自己刻名字。"},{"pid":"2eebe1eee6cfc28042a1358ba3ba956a19ac9e2d","tid":2261531,"uid":331421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"但由於考取內地記者證需時很長，香港局勢變化非常快，「我便破例獲得前往香港採訪的機會，<br />\n<br />\n啫係無牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無牌記者"},{"pid":"4e6f67cd532e97827413211876a77c1b7ce313d2","tid":2261531,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"法官算唔算違反國安法<br />\n詆毁中國司法系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}